# Current phase: Phase 1 — Core shop, no payments yet

## What is in scope RIGHT NOW
- Homepage with hero, categories, featured products
- Product listing page with category filter
- Product detail page
- Shopping cart (Zustand, client-side only)
- Checkout form (name, phone, address, PIN — no payment gateway yet)
- Order saved to Supabase, confirmation email via Resend
- Admin panel at `/admin` — upload products, view orders, update stock
- Cloudinary image upload in admin

## What is OUT OF SCOPE in Phase 1 — do not build, do not scaffold
- Razorpay or any payment gateway
- Customer login / authentication
- Order tracking page
- Wishlist
- Reviews
- SMS / WhatsApp integration
- Analytics dashboard
- Coupons or discount codes

## Phase 1 database tables (only these, nothing more)
- `products` — id, name, slug, description, price, stock, category, images (text[]), is_published
- `categories` — id, name, slug
- `orders` — id, customer_name, phone, address, pin_code, city, state, items (jsonb), total, status, created_at
- `admin_users` — id, email (single row, you are the only admin)

## Definition of done for Phase 1
- [ ] Customer can browse, filter, and view products
- [ ] Customer can add to cart and place an order (cash on delivery)
- [ ] Admin can log in, upload products with photos, and see incoming orders
- [ ] Deployed and live on Vercel with a custom domain
